#About me
I’m Mohamed Amine Bergach a passionate computer engineer, after graduating from Telecom SudParis (France) in 2011, I’m preparing my Phd at Inria, I expects to finish this year 2015.
My interests include GPU architecture, GPGPU applications, OpenCL, Signal processing, Image processing, Electronics and security.

I'm Fluent on OpenCL, C, C++ and Arabic.



Thanks,

Mohamed Amine BERGACH
